Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.54,0:01:50.54,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(500,500)}翻譯：spirit ZERO；後期：zipwinmax。
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.74,0:00:22.84,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哼哼哼  大吃一驚了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.15,0:00:24.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然是我藏在裡面…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.79,0:00:26.65,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你們做什麼  真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.87,0:00:28.78,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,閒著的話就過來幫我打掃
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.29,0:00:32.79,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（小朝倉早上太忙了沒工夫搭理他倆）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.21,0:00:48.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,真是的  長門同學你呀
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.36,0:00:50.11,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,玩過了也不收起來
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.24,0:00:53.71,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（主婦模式下的小朝倉不好對付）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.80,0:00:54.95,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}（亮晶晶）
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.29,0:00:57.45,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哦  變得好乾淨了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.00,0:01:00.48,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,太高的地方我自己夠不著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.76,0:01:02.31,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝你幫忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.87,0:01:06.33,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,接下來差不多該去準備午飯了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.81,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,黃綠先生  過來幫我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.10,0:01:09.91,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.29,0:01:14.18,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,現在加入胡椒鹽
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.49,0:01:15.14,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.35,0:01:20.13,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,謝謝  多虧了黃綠先生進展迅速
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.31,0:01:24.81,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,（兩人好像被小朝倉所征服了）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:24.81,0:01:26.77,zhushi,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,{\fad(0,500)}（三點）
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.27,0:01:26.60,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:27.59,0:01:30.36,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,兩個人今天都幫了我很多
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.95,0:01:35.67,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,說起來  黃綠先生這打扮是怎麼回事
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.22,0:01:40.10,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你穿上這個就明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.80,0:01:41.53,zhengwen,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,哈？
